data.description:
Welcome home to this charming ranch-style home, move-in ready and boasting a host of desirable features! With 3 bedrooms (1 non-conforming) 2 full bathrooms, and a 2-car garage this home offers both comfort and convenience.
Step inside to discover a beautiful interior, complete with a brand new roof and stunning granite countertops in the kitchen. Enjoy the comfort of central air conditioning and a newer furnace ensuring year round comfort.
Outside , the newly landscaped backyard offers a serene retreat perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The new front door, sliding door and back door not only enhance curb appeal but also add a touch of modern elegance to the home.
Additionally the home comes with all appliances including a newer washer and dryer, on demand hot water heater and a brand new skylight just to name a few of the updates. 
This home is move in ready so you can start enjoying your new home right away!
